Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.23,0:00:03.89,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur6}不必消去这份记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.89,0:00:05.92,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}人生不是还很漫长？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.27,0:00:08.91,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur6}那些没有做完的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.91,0:00:12.55,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur6}只是想重新做起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.57,0:00:28.81,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur6}明明一直在追赶着梦的延续
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.29,0:00:35.14,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur6}跌跌撞撞地走在弯曲的小道上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.14,0:00:38.30,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}不奢望回到那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.30,0:00:41.82,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}只是在苦寻那片丢失的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.82,0:00:43.48,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}就像你明白一样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.48,0:00:48.70,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}除去那像牺牲之后的悲伤表情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.70,0:00:50.41,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}罪孽之后并不是泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.41,0:00:52.08,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}而是一直以来背负的苦难
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.08,0:00:53.73,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}迷失在没有出口的情感迷宫中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.73,0:00:55.42,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}在等待着谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.42,0:00:57.22,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}就像在白色笔记本上刻画一样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.22,0:00:58.95,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}很想诚实地说出心声
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.95,0:01:00.64,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}在逃避什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.64,0:01:02.25,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}…原来是叫做现实的东西吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.25,0:01:05.60,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}为了实现愿望而活着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.60,0:01:09.01,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}不禁想要大喊  你能听到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.01,0:01:13.15,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur6}平安无事却让人没法接受
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.11,0:01:15.92,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}…无家可归
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.92,0:01:19.24,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}感谢同伴们带来的温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.24,0:01:21.66,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur6}所以要更加坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.60,0:01:24.57,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}让人怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.57,0:01:27.81,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)\blur6}这种痛苦也不赖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.48,0:22:32.98,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)\blur6}那天看到的绯红天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.98,0:22:38.22,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}你还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.22,0:22:44.12,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}约定和契约  被初夏的微风所怀抱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.12,0:22:48.39,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur6}两个人互相依靠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.91,0:22:57.42,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur6}在强颜欢笑的背后
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.42,0:23:02.81,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}隐藏着逐渐扩大的阴谋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.81,0:23:12.07,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur6}所以  只装做没有发现  选择了重生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.70,0:23:21.60,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur6}在桌边继续等待那没有震撼的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.20,0:23:29.96,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur6}在空白的夜里  无法迎接的黎明
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.96,0:23:34.73,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}其实我全部都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.73,0:23:40.36,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}那天看到的绯红天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.36,0:23:45.27,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}总有一天会想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.27,0:23:51.12,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}抱着没有实现的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.12,0:23:55.38,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur6}两个人一起出发
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.11,0:01:35.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了追求贤者之石的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.84,0:01:39.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潜入原第五研究所的爱德和阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.70,0:01:44.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遇到了把灵魂固定在铠甲上的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.34,0:01:47.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在战斗中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.80,0:01:49.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为66号所说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.26,0:01:58.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔怀疑自己是不是爱德所制造的虚假灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.96,0:02:02.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,950)\fn方正大标宋_GBK\fs135\fsp12\blur6\bord5\1c&H00&\3c&HFFFFFFFF&}被制造出来的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.70,0:02:06.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经能起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.87,0:02:10.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第五研究所呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.53,0:02:11.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.28,0:02:13.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知被什么人炸毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.07,0:02:15.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不留一点痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.38,0:02:17.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 全部泡汤了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.00,0:02:21.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.70,0:02:23.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.41,0:02:27.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差一点就抓住真实了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.73,0:02:30.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不是住院的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.94,0:02:34.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢之炼金术师阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.31,0:02:37.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事先向您道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.83,0:02:38.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.44,0:02:47.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自作主张
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.16,0:02:50.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弄不好就在那里丢了性命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.76,0:02:54.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要什么都想自己来做
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.54,0:02:56.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多依赖一下周围的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.04,0:03:03.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再多信任大人们一些有什么不好？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.65,0:03:09.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.21,0:03:12.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不符合军衔的粗言和暴力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.04,0:03:14.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.15,0:03:17.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.81,0:03:20.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.54,0:03:23.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打耳光的责罚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.91,0:03:26.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种东西 没有 没有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.84,0:03:29.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么那么在意？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.96,0:03:33.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国家炼金术师相当于军队里的少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.47,0:03:38.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是为了那种东西才获得国家资格的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.28,0:03:41.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没必要用敬语
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.81,0:03:42.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.94,0:03:45.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么在意真是亏了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.72,0:03:46.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,适应得真快
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.74,0:03:49.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 阿尔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.41,0:03:52.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔冯斯的话 刚才 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.91,0:03:54.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,架起拳头教训过他了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.77,0:03:56.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.49,0:04:02.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有一个要被骂一顿的盛大活动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.28,0:04:10.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 这里是假肢道具商人——洛克贝尔家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.61,0:04:13.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱德？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.69,0:04:16.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打电话过来真是稀奇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.82,0:04:20.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 虽然很难开口 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.85,0:04:23.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能来中央都市出差？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.84,0:04:24.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出差？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.06,0:04:25.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.19,0:04:27.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,右臂呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.98,0:04:29.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手指虽然能动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.39,0:04:31.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是完全无法抬高手臂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.10,0:04:38.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然不行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.74,0:04:39.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.50,0:04:40.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 我这里的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.02,0:04:44.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在不能动之前干了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.36,0:04:48.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,华丽地打了一场
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.30,0:04:53.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这小子把我的机械铠当什么来用了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.83,0:05:02.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 喂喂 温莉？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.08,0:05:04.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真拿你没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.52,0:05:05.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在中央都市的哪个地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.42,0:05:09.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好像今天特别温…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.81,0:05:12.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.20,0:05:16.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.96,0:05:18.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.09,0:05:22.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给女朋友打电话？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.26,0:05:24.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么女朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.94,0:05:27.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么呀 真没意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.89,0:05:29.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在你这个年龄的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.70,0:05:30.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.18,0:05:33.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那种地方干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.23,0:05:35.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.76,0:05:37.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.12,0:05:39.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不去房间里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.24,0:05:49.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没事 你先去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.62,0:06:12.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.22,0:06:21.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会是被你哥哥做出来的铠甲人偶吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.88,0:06:32.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,屁股好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.47,0:06:36.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱德他们居然能坐这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.38,0:06:41.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是在西边出口设立了标志
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.58,0:06:43.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就能知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.37,0:06:47.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿姆斯壮少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.04,0:06:52.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温莉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.52,0:06:56.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾尔利克那对笨蛋兄弟呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.41,0:06:59.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事实上…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.00,0:07:07.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱德住院了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.67,0:07:12.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真 真快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.21,0:07:16.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来是准备收特急费用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.90,0:07:21.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为 我没有好好整备
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.62,0:07:22.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机械铠才坏掉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.13,0:07:25.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,导致你受了这么重的伤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.79,0:07:32.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是温莉的错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.72,0:07:35.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来就是我的用法太粗暴了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.08,0:07:38.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整备就像以前一样很完美
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.31,0:07:42.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他没有注意到螺丝没上好？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.38,0:07:47.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且因为手臂坏掉了反而还少受了伤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.57,0:07:50.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.15,0:07:52.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果全都好？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.98,0:07:57.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 马上谈谈我出差维修的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.91,0:07:59.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然要附加特急费用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.15,0:08:05.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牛奶…留下了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.81,0:08:09.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我讨厌牛奶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.91,0:08:13.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你老是这样 所以始终是个小豆丁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.94,0:08:14.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.87,0:08:16.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌的东西就是讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.21,0:08:20.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太任性了 爱德华·艾尔利克
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.11,0:08:22.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小孩子们都喝的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.34,0:08:25.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不喝牛奶的话是不会受欢迎的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.09,0:08:27.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.09,0:08:38.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔那家伙最近很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.07,0:08:42.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.99,0:08:46.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像有什么烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.31,0:09:04.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊 不会是被你哥哥做出来的铠甲人偶吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.94,0:09:07.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,承认吧 那样就轻松了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.74,0:09:17.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 维修完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.31,0:09:19.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.41,0:09:21.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总算修好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.49,0:09:23.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.01,0:09:25.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.99,0:09:28.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟 爱德
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.69,0:09:31.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说你把女人带进病房打情骂俏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.22,0:09:35.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她只是普通的机械铠维修师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.98,0:09:38.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把维修师骗进怀里了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.23,0:09:42.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一搭话就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.12,0:09:44.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫马斯·休斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.27,0:09:46.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.44,0:09:47.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫温莉·洛克贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.56,0:09:50.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这样好吗 又旷工
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.60,0:09:52.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.50,0:09:54.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我让谢丝卡留下加班了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.87,0:09:57.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是魔鬼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.69,0:10:01.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 你们马上就不需要让护卫保护了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.18,0:10:02.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.72,0:10:04.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,护卫是？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.29,0:10:08.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你在做什么危险的事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.26,0:10:11.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.03,0:10:12.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.79,0:10:17.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么大不了的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.48,0:10:29.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 反正问你们也是白问
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.26,0:10:33.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.79,0:10:36.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去找个旅馆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.49,0:10:40.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？那就住我家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.29,0:10:41.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.97,0:10:43.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.34,0:10:45.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老婆和女儿都会高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.21,0:10:45.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.71,0:10:46.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 就这么决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.19,0:10:48.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.42,0:10:49.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来来 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.57,0:10:53.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.79,0:11:03.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚 生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.22,0:11:08.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那个 休斯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.78,0:11:10.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.89,0:11:12.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问得好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.28,0:11:15.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是艾莉西亚的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.41,0:11:17.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生日呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.20,0:11:22.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚几岁了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.91,0:11:23.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.76,0:11:26.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三岁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.93,0:11:27.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.82,0:11:28.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.57,0:11:30.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.49,0:11:43.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和他们从小就在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.70,0:11:45.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像姐弟一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.85,0:11:48.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们总是那副德行 很让人担心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.95,0:11:50.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.45,0:11:52.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶尔回来一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.22,0:11:53.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果手臂去见佛祖了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.70,0:12:00.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被叫出来一看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.39,0:12:02.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱德受了那么重的伤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.39,0:12:04.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔又在烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.50,0:12:08.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 到底出了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.06,0:12:10.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们绝对不会告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.31,0:12:12.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离开利塞布尔的时候也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.39,0:12:17.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为没有商量的必要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.54,0:12:20.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们觉得温莉的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.55,0:12:23.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不说也会明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.79,0:12:31.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 不说出口就无法传达的事情也是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.84,0:12:35.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.29,0:12:40.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男人是那种比起语言来更擅长用行动来表现的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.54,0:12:45.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛苦的事情 尽量不想让其他人来背负
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.22,0:12:48.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不想让人担心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.54,0:12:49.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才不说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.89,0:12:53.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.09,0:12:55.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果那对兄弟说了泄气话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.43,0:13:00.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候就要好好地接受
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.31,0:13:02.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样不也挺好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.95,0:13:08.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚 一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.72,0:13:09.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要下去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.10,0:13:11.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 请
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.84,0:13:16.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么呀 艾莉西亚要和我玩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.48,0:13:18.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.21,0:13:18.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}女儿很受欢迎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.42,0:13:20.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.98,0:13:23.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 小鬼们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.77,0:13:25.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我女儿出手的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.34,0:13:26.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会让你们吃不了兜着走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.19,0:13:28.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用行动表现过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.31,0:13:35.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.93,0:13:39.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在中央市的这段时间一直住下去也没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.80,0:13:41.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能麻烦您那么久…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.40,0:13:46.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她完全喜欢上你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.41,0:13:50.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么看着 就像姐妹一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.37,0:13:52.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.83,0:13:53.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.27,0:13:55.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早点回来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.01,0:13:58.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的住宿也决定了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.83,0:14:05.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是有了个妹妹 好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.19,0:14:13.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也出现了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.35,0:14:15.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.34,0:14:20.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥还拥有真实的身体 所以
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.84,0:14:23.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不喝是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.38,0:14:26.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌的东西就是讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.87,0:14:29.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我也有在长高
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.31,0:14:32.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却老是说我矮子 矮子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.99,0:14:35.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.11,0:14:38.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体那么高大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.64,0:14:44.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不希望自己的身体变成这个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.97,0:14:48.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.28,0:14:52.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得也是 是我害你变成这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.58,0:14:56.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我希望尽快让你恢复原状
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.09,0:14:58.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的能够保证我能恢复原状吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.94,0:15:01.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会让你恢复原状的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.83,0:15:02.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.99,0:15:03.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“相信”你？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.48,0:15:07.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个空荡荡的身体叫我相信什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.24,0:15:11.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实“记忆”只不过是一些“情报”而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.26,0:15:14.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以还是能用人工的方式构筑的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.26,0:15:17.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.21,0:15:17.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.11,0:15:21.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你之前不是说有件事因为太过害怕而一直没跟我说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.21,0:15:23.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你要跟我说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.02,0:15:24.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.41,0:15:26.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灵魂和记忆…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.22,0:15:30.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都是假造的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.41,0:15:35.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温莉和婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.91,0:15:38.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是在骗我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.16,0:15:42.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.95,0:15:49.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一直都在想这些事情吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.66,0:15:56.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想说的话都说完了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.03,0:16:02.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.57,0:16:14.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱德
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.41,0:16:16.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱德
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.64,0:16:20.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔你这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.42,0:16:23.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.96,0:16:27.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干嘛突然打我？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.14,0:16:34.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温莉？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.15,0:16:36.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔你这个大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.63,0:16:39.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本不明白爱德的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.73,0:16:43.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱德害怕得不敢说的事情是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.75,0:16:47.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是在恨他的这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.65,0:16:53.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.21,0:16:57.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他已经无法吃饭和睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.66,0:17:00.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也感觉不到疼痛了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.16,0:17:03.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对在恨我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.95,0:17:06.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔不会恨你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.02,0:17:08.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去问他就知道了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.59,0:17:11.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.13,0:17:13.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害怕得不敢去问
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.11,0:17:17.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.03,0:17:20.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而你居然对他…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.03,0:17:21.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.13,0:17:30.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这世上哪有会冒着自己的生命危险去假造弟弟的笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.80,0:17:36.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们不是相依为命的两兄弟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.93,0:17:42.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去追
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.95,0:17:46.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用跑的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.11,0:17:47.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.84,0:18:04.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.16,0:18:05.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.02,0:18:09.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有段时间没交手了 身体变迟钝了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.66,0:18:20.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.00,0:18:23.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…等一下 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.30,0:18:26.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.10,0:18:29.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伤口会裂开的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.43,0:18:38.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胜了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.45,0:18:41.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次胜了你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.36,0:18:45.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好狡猾 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.67,0:18:49.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啰嗦 胜了就是胜了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.71,0:18:53.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小时候开始就经常吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.57,0:18:55.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.82,0:18:58.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在回想起来 全是因为些小事而吵架呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.43,0:19:02.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,争夺双层床的上下位置之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.12,0:19:06.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为零食的事情也吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.28,0:19:07.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相互抢玩具也干过
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.10,0:19:09.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.48,0:19:10.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在雷茵河玩的时候也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.17,0:19:13.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被推进河里了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.45,0:19:15.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修行中也吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.81,0:19:18.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被说“吵死了” 差点没被师傅杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.86,0:19:20.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那应该是平局吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.89,0:19:23.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们曾经为了“谁能娶温莉”这件事打过架呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.14,0:19:25.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？那个我不记得了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.17,0:19:27.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.63,0:19:28.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 被甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.03,0:19:30.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.48,0:19:41.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认为这些全部都是假的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.06,0:19:42.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.47,0:19:46.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说过“无论如何都要让自己的身体恢复原状”
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.80,0:19:48.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种心情也是制造出来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.56,0:19:50.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是制造出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.34,0:19:52.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.01,0:19:55.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已经决定了 一定要取回原来的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.95,0:19:57.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不断向前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.45,0:20:02.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向前进 让心灵和实力变得越来越强
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.24,0:20:04.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牛奶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.96,0:20:05.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.78,0:20:07.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽量吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.51,0:20:11.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们越来越强吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.84,0:20:14.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休斯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.81,0:20:19.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然有些事不说出口的话就没法传达呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.80,0:20:22.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.37,0:20:41.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.48,0:20:43.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.22,0:20:46.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.50,0:20:47.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.70,0:20:51.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是伊修瓦尔人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.99,0:20:52.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失敬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.49,0:20:55.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忘记和你打招呼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.86,0:20:58.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是负责歼灭这个地区的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.73,0:21:01.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国家炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.67,0:21:10.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.75,0:21:12.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.20,0:21:16.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,东方之都郊外的贫民窟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.85,0:21:20.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老先生 你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.65,0:21:23.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你一样是伊修瓦尔人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.16,0:21:25.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.20,0:21:27.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不会出卖自己人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.26,0:21:32.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里还有别的伊修瓦尔人的幸存者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.05,0:21:33.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.59,0:21:36.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使是在这到处是煤烟味的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.61,0:21:38.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住起来也算是不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.87,0:21:45.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为“整个世界都是我们伊修瓦拉神的胸怀”呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.86,0:21:48.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.80,0:21:51.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要逞强
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.64,0:21:54.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你全身受伤从下水道里漂过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.09,0:22:06.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问 我的右手还在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.98,0:22:08.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 还在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.22,0:22:14.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真厉害 这个刺青
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.51,0:22:23.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是从家人那里得到的重要羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.16,0:24:01.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挚友最终成为了战友
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.17,0:24:05.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理所当然地待在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.79,0:24:10.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使谈论的未来 现在暗淡得犹如灰色
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.18,0:24:13.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挚友还像往常一样在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.94,0:24:17.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回 钢之炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.22,0:24:18.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fullmetal Alchemist
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.85,0:24:21.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第10话 各自的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.77,0:24:24.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理所当然的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.52,0:24:27.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是无可替代的东西
